{"tid":2259341,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"人權律師常瑋平失去聯絡 父親和代表律師促公安交代","createTime":"2020-10-26T17:46:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-27T08:49:27.000Z","uid":240362,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"7d94a5c31058bad20014e339c0985b47ced518bf","tid":2259341,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:46:35.000Z","msg":"曾代理多宗公民權益案件的陝西人權律師常瑋平，去年底被指涉及危害國家安全，一直在陝西家鄕處於取保候審狀態，近日還自拍影片透露自己被關押期間曾遭受酷刑。不過，該影片上載網不久後，常瑋平於上周四在家鄉再次失聯，他的父親和律師早上到公安局，要求當局交代細節。<br />\n<br />\n香港電台引述常瑋平的代表律師張庭源表示，早上向3名便衣警員提出要求交代常瑋平是否已被正式立案、涉及的強制措施等，並向公安申請會見常瑋平，及爭取取保候審。<br />\n<br />\n常瑋平於本月16日自拍影片上載到YouTube，他強調自己去年參與廈門聚會，並未違反中國法律，也堅信自己無罪。常又提到被逮捕後，受到寶雞市公安的酷刑對待。他說：「我被鎖在保泰賓館招待所的房間內的老虎凳上，每天24小時，長達10天。這是一種極端的酷刑，對我造成的傷害是，我右手的食指與無名指到現在依然麻木，沒有知覺或知覺不正常。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/G2PROBFVZRE75OAKAV5EGNYUBM/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FG2PROBFVZRE75OAKAV5EGNYUBM%2F&d=PtGeCDSqwX4ndXcvBPlETdagwJJ%2BwSr9lfhZhsTZPo0%3D&h=b6649a3c\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fchina%2F20201026%2FG2PROBFVZRE75OAKAV5EGNYUBM%2F&h=1cfc29ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/china/20201026/G2PROBFVZRE75OAKAV5EGNYUBM/</a>"},{"pid":"d3fb955d91dad5062f3902c2dd2f7807bdd04d94","tid":2259341,"uid":126919,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:47:55.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n10日"},{"pid":"ffac9b1b65c2d4072ea343cb4a1dd8b1d8e6e661","tid":2259341,"uid":203889,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-26T17:48:26.000Z","msg":"<span class=\"small\">612就黎冇錢啦<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/2257791\" data-auto-link ta